org.enterprisedomain.classmaker

Interface ClassMakerPlant

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClassMakerPlantImpl

    public interface ClassMakerPlant
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Plant'. ClassMaker API facade service.

    The following features are supported:

    • Workspace
    • SCM Registry
    See Also:
    ClassMakerPackage.getClassMakerPlant()
